  └── src/ingestion/     (offline) Load → Chunk → Clean → Index
{% endif %}
{% if profile in ["agent", "full"] %}
src/workflows/    Agent loop (ReAct / Planner-Executor / Multi-agent)
  ├── src/agents/        Agent definitions
  ├── src/tools/         Pluggable tools
  ├── src/memory/        Short-term + long-term memory
  └── src/retrieval/     RAG subsystem for agents
{% endif %}
    │
    ▼
src/monitoring/   Trace spans + Prometheus metrics
    │
    ▼
Response
```

## Modules
{% if profile in ["rag", "full"] %}
### Ingestion (`src/ingestion/`)
Offline pipeline to prepare documents for retrieval.
- `loader.py` — load from PDF, web, files, databases
- `chunker.py` — split documents into retrieval chunks
- `cleaner.py` — normalise, deduplicate, filter noise

### Embedding (`src/embedding/`)
- `embedder.py` — wraps the `{{ embedding_model }}` model; produces vectors
- `utils.py` — batching helpers and similarity utilities

### Vector Store (`src/vectorstore/`)
Interfaces with `{{ vector_db }}`.
- `client.py` — connection management
- `indexer.py` — batch upsert embeddings
- `retriever.py` — top-k similarity search

### RAG Core (`src/rag/`)
End-to-end retrieval-augmented generation.
- `pipeline.py` — orchestrates retrieve → rerank → generate
- `prompt.py` — prompt templates and formatters
- `generator.py` — `{{ llm_provider }}` / `{{ llm_model }}` wrapper
{% endif %}
{% if profile in ["agent", "full"] %}
### Agents (`src/agents/`)
- `base_agent.py` — abstract agent interface
- `chat_agent.py` — conversational agent
- `planner_agent.py` — decomposes goals into tasks
- `executor_agent.py` — executes tool-use actions

### Tools (`src/tools/`)
Pluggable capability extensions for agents.
- `web_search.py` — live internet search
- `calculator.py` — safe arithmetic evaluation
- `db_tool.py` — structured database queries
- `rag_tool.py` — RAG retrieval as a tool

### LLM (`src/llm/`)
- `client.py` — unified `{{ llm_provider }}` client
- `prompts.py` — prompt construction helpers
- `output_parser.py` — structured output parsing

### Memory (`src/memory/`)
- `short_term.py` — conversation buffer
- `long_term.py` — vector DB knowledge store
- `episodic.py` — task / session memory

### Workflows (`src/workflows/`)
- `agent_loop.py` — ReAct think → act → observe loop
- `planner_executor.py` — Plan → Execute pattern
- `multi_agent.py` — multi-agent coordination
{% endif %}

### API (`src/api/`)
FastAPI layer.
- `routes.py` — endpoint definitions
- `schemas.py` — Pydantic request / response models
- `controllers.py` — business logic called by routes

### Cache (`src/cache/`)
- `redis_client.py` — Redis connection and semantic cache helpers

### Monitoring (`src/monitoring/`)
- `tracing.py` — OpenTelemetry span instrumentation
- `metrics.py` — Prometheus counter / histogram definitions

### Config (`src/configs/`)
- `config.py` — `Settings` class (pydantic-settings, reads `.env`)

### Utils (`src/utils/`)
- `logger.py` — structured logging setup
- `helpers.py` — shared utilities
